<i>noun</i>: 상제 [상제], 문상객 [문ː상객] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>상제 [상제]</dt><br>
<dd>mourner</dd><br>
<dd>부모나 조부모가 죽어서 상중에 있는 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>A person who is in mourning for his/her parents or grandparents.</dd><br>
<dt>문상객 [문ː상객]</dt><br>
<dd>mourner</dd><br>
<dd>애도의 뜻을 나타내고 상주를 위로하러 초상집에 찾아온 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>A person visiting a family in mourning in order to comfort the chief mourner with one's condolences.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>